  "knowledge_nodes": [
    {
      "content": "理想化的无空气阻力真空环境，只保留重力作用。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_7cb2cd1fcc29c300",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "setting.vacuum",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "日常经验中，重的石头确实比轻的羽毛下落得快。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_e951ad3967e72014",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.daily",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在水、油等不同介质中比较轻重物体下落，   介质越稠密速度差异越大，越稀薄差异越小。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_28cef2d83203bb1d",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.media",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在空气中做精细实验，重量差异较大的物体   几乎同时落地，轻微差异可归因于空气阻力。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_f51f07c2cd23fa08",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.air",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "伽利略斜面实验显示：不同重量小球在相同斜面条件下   呈现近似一致的加速趋势。",
      "kind": "observation",
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": {
        "prior": 0.9
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_3a8b4c5691b7875a",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "obs.inclined_plane",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "物体下落速度与重量成正比：重物比轻物下落更快。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_2e2762bf27535603",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.A",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "假设重物下落更快，将重球 H 与轻球 L 绑在一起，   L 拖拽 H，复合体 HL 速度应慢于 H 单独下落。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_39caaacc70ea5355",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.T1",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "假设重物下落更快，复合体 HL 总重量大于 H，   因此 HL 速度应快于 H 单独下落。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_57630db8b7a6ae3c",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.T2",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "T1 与 T2 互相矛盾：复合体 HL 不能同时慢于 H 又快于 H。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "contradiction",
      "metadata": {
        "between": [
          "hyp.T1",
          "hyp.T2"
        ]
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_0c93352125171984",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "rel.T1_contra_T2",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "按亚里士多德定律，在真空中也应重者下落更快。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_49b6c4db6dd2b9fe",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.A_vac",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "综合介质和空气实验的证据，   在真空中不同重量物体应以相同速率下落。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_f758caaeaa2b8241",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.V",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验提供了正面证据：在真空中物体等速下落。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_c2d990723ea82a5b",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "hyp.V_inclined",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "两条独立证据链得出等价的真空等速结论。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "equivalence",
      "metadata": {
        "between": [
          "hyp.V",
          "hyp.V_inclined"
        ]
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_4e9a0a3853a8526b",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "rel.V_equiv",
          "module": "default",
          "package": "galileo_coarse",
          "version": "4.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "真空中不能同时 \" 重者更快 \" 又 \" 等速下落 \" 。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "contradiction",
      "metadata": {
        "between": [
          "hyp.A_vac",
